Mario Balotelli was back at the Etihad Stadium on Monday, to watch  his new Liverpool side go down 3-1 to former club Manchester City.

The Italian spent two-and-a-half-years at City, and  returned to his old ground to watch the Manchester City vs Liverpool clash.

An excited Balotelli took to Instagram to share a picture of himself on the way to the game, with fellow Reds Jon Flanagan and Adam Lallana. 

